headline: Wall Street Firms Echo Trimble Inc. (TRMB) Growth Prospects on Improving Macroeconomics
summary: Trimble Inc. (NASDAQ:TRMB) is one of the best fertilizer stocks to invest in. On December 16, KeyBanc upgraded Trimble Inc. (NASDAQ:TRMB) to an Overweight from Sector Weight and set a $99 price target. The upgrade underscores the research firm’s confidence in the company’s prospects, with low-teens annual recurring revenue and a double-digit earnings-per-share growth framework. […]
